      <odd id="aspace_df2b11332b77ed41f4ff62ddfbe33faf">
         <head>General note</head>
         <p>Forms part of Yale Record Group 32-E (YRG 32-E), Records of Yale University Library programs, projects, and committees.</p>  
      </odd>
      <accessrestrict id="aspace_44a89e093994da6fee8d589889d9245b">
