         <p>The materials are open for research.</p>  
      </accessrestrict>
      <separatedmaterial id="aspace_2934fa122f831bdbb9fe11a2e4e1b380">
         <head>Separated Materials</head>
         <p>8 folders containing original letters and cables to, and copies of letters and cables from, Lt. Col. Ralph H. Isham, being his correspondence with Joyce Lady Talbot and others concerning the purchase of the Boswell papers were returned to donor, June 2008.</p>  
      </separatedmaterial>
      <prefercite id="aspace_4a45a3f46a2d0312e6999e2484bde851">
